                                text="&lt;p>&lt;span class=&quot;light-font&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;body-unica-32-reg&quot;>At AbbVie, we bring our energy and tenacity to work every day, finding new and better ways to help people around the world.&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
