                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="singarx"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>Whether you work in the office, in the field or a combination of both, the objective is the same—to make a real difference in people’s lives. That’s why we continually ask questions and champion new perspectives, building on each other’s expertise to develop the best solutions for the people who depend on us. Learn more about our teams and their impact. &lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
